---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Summer School - AARC"
  description="The AARC Summer School on Robotics and Automation in Africa - promoting robotics education and research across the continent."
>

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-12 pb-24 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="reveal mb-16">
      <a href="/" class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
        Back to home
      </a>
      <p class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Summer School 2027</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight"><span class="nasal-title">AARC</span> Summer School</h1>
      <p class="mb-8 text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-300 leading-snug">on Robotics &amp; Automation in Africa</p>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-400">
        An initiative to promote robotics education and research in South Africa and across the continent -
        filling a critical gap for early-stage robotics researchers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- About -->
    <div class="reveal panel rounded-3xl p-8 mb-10">
      <p class="mb-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-orange-300/80">About</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-white">About the Initiative</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
        The field of robotics is steadily growing in South Africa, which is home to some of the largest
        robotics and machine learning labs in Africa. Despite this, there are currently no active summer
        schools aimed at early-stage robotics researchers. The AARC Summer School is poised to fill this
        important gap - bringing together graduate students, researchers, and practitioners for an intensive
        programme of keynotes, tutorials, and hands-on sessions.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
        The school will take place in <strong class="text-white">August/September 2027</strong>. We aim to
        co-locate with the <strong class="text-white">Deep Learning Indaba</strong>, with whom the organising
        committee has an existing relationship and which is expected to take place in South Africa next year.
        By co-locating with the largest ongoing machine learning and AI conference in Africa, we hope to
        expand the reach of our school to include participants from across the continent - promoting robotics
        education and building a research community on a much larger scale.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-orange-400/15 bg-orange-400/5 p-5">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-orange-200">At a Glance</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span><strong class="text-white">When:</strong>&nbsp;August/September 2027 (exact dates TBC)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span><strong class="text-white">Where:</strong>&nbsp;South Africa</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span><strong class="text-white">Duration:</strong>&nbsp;3 days</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span><strong class="text-white">Target Audience:</strong>&nbsp;Graduate students with a background in ML/AI</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Areas of Interest -->
    <div class="reveal mb-4">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Areas of Interest</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">What to expect</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-400">
        The summer school will cover foundational and cutting-edge areas in robotics and automation. Exact topics and session details will be confirmed as the programme is finalized.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal panel rounded-3xl p-8 mb-10">
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">ROS2 and Robotics Foundations</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Essential tools and frameworks for modern robotics development</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Robot Control and Autonomy</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Techniques for enabling autonomous robot decision-making and control</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Perception and Sensor Integration</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Processing sensor data for robot understanding of the environment</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-orange-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">SLAM and Navigation</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Simultaneous localization, mapping, and autonomous navigation</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Behaviour Design and Decision-Making</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Cognitive and intelligent robotics, planning, and reasoning</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Sim-to-Real Transfer</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Bridging simulation and real-world robot deployment</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">HRI and Natural Language Interaction</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Human-robot interaction and language-based communication</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-400"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Real-World Robotics Applications</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Practical deployments across industries, agriculture, and service sectors</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Programme Schedule -->
    <div class="reveal mb-4">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Programme & Schedule</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Three-day agenda</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-400">
        The programme features keynote lectures, hands-on sessions, panel discussions, and networking opportunities. Daily sessions run from 08:30 to 17:00. This schedule is tentative and subject to change.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal mb-10 overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
            <th class="py-3 px-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-300/80 text-left w-[140px]">Time</th>
            <th class="py-3 px-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-300/80 text-center">Day 1</th>
            <th class="py-3 px-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-300/80 text-center">Day 2</th>
            <th class="py-3 px-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-300/80 text-center">Day 3</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/5 text-slate-300">
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">08:30 – 09:00</td>
            <td rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center">Registration</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center">Registration</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center">Registration</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">09:00 – 09:30</td>
            <td rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-orange-200/90">Keynote</td>
            <td rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-orange-200/90">Keynote</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">09:30 – 10:00</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-white font-semibold">Welcome Session</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">10:00 – 10:30</td>
            <td colspan="3" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-slate-500 italic">Coffee Break</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">10:30 – 11:00</td>
            <td rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-orange-200/90">Keynote</td>
            <td rowspan="3" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-cyan-300/80">Hands-on Session:<br/><span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Robot Perception</span></td>
            <td rowspan="3" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-emerald-300/80">Poster Session</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">11:00 – 11:30</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">11:30 – 12:00</td>
            <td rowspan="3" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-cyan-300/80">Hands-on Session:<br/><span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Introduction to ROS</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">12:00 – 12:30</td>
            <td rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-orange-200/90">Keynote</td>
            <td rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-orange-200/90">Keynote</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">12:30 – 13:00</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">13:00 – 13:30</td>
            <td colspan="3" rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-slate-500 italic">Lunch Break</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">13:30 – 14:00</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">14:00 – 14:30</td>
            <td rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-orange-200/90">Keynote</td>
            <td rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-orange-200/90">Keynote</td>
            <td rowspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-orange-200/90">Keynote</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">14:30 – 15:00</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">15:00 – 15:30</td>
            <td rowspan="4" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-cyan-300/80">Hands-on Session:<br/><span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Robot Learning Challenge</span><br/><br/><span class="text-xs text-amber-300/70">Robotics lab visit:</span><br/><span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Visit to the Wits University RAIL Lab</span></td>
            <td rowspan="4" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-violet-300/80">Panel Discussion</td>
            <td rowspan="3" class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-cyan-300/80">Hands-on Session:<br/><span class="text-xs text-slate-500">RoboCup</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">15:30 – 16:00</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">16:00 – 16:30</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-slate-400 whitespace-nowrap">16:30 – 17:00</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-4 text-center text-white font-semibold">Closing Session</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Potential Speakers -->
    <div class="reveal mb-4">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Speakers</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Potential Speakers</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-400">
        The school will feature 8 keynote talks and a panel session. The tentative list of speakers is as follows.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 mb-10">

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="/images/people/amir.jpg" alt="Amir Patel" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Amir Patel</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">Biomechanics · Robotics</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            Associate Professor at UCL studying how animals achieve agility and speed, applying those insights to robotics. His work spans sensor fusion, computer vision, and optimal control for measuring and modelling locomotion, with applications in ecology, disease monitoring, and sports science.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="https://cifar.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Benjamin-Rosman-.jpg" alt="Benjamin Rosman" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Benjamin Rosman</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">RL · Intelligence</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            Professor at the University of the Witwatersrand and founding Director of the MIND Institute. Runs the RAIL Laboratory and serves as Chief Science Officer of Lelapa AI, building AI for Africans, by Africans.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="/images/people/david.jpg" alt="David Vernon" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">David Vernon</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">Cognitive Robotics</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            Over forty years in robotics and twenty in cognitive robotics. Technical coordinator behind the iCub open-source cognitive humanoid robot, founding co-chair of the IEEE RAS Technical Committee for Cognitive Robotics, and author of four books on robotics and cognitive systems.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="https://cs.brown.edu/people/gdk/images/gdk-photo3.jpg" alt="George Konidaris" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">George Konidaris</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">AI · Robot Intelligence</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            Associate Professor of Computer Science and director of the Intelligent Robot Lab at Brown University. Co-founder of Realtime Robotics and Lelapa AI. His research focuses on understanding the fundamental computational processes that generate intelligence and using them to design a generally-intelligent robot.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="https://africanroboticsunit.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/paulamayo.jpg" alt="Paul Amayo" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Paul Amayo</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">Robotics · Education</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            Senior Lecturer and Principal Investigator at the University of Cape Town with broad experience from self-driving cars in the UK to para-transit in Kenya. Passionate about advancing technology through research and ensuring its adoption in communities where it would do the most good.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="https://www.raillab.org/author/pravesh-ranchod/avatar_hua31b2412db95e26580ae27fdabc849c6_1812768_270x270_fill_q75_lanczos_center.jpg" alt="Pravesh Ranchod" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Pravesh Ranchod</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">Skill Discovery · LfD</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            Works in Learning from Demonstration with a focus on Skill Discovery - decomposing expert demonstrations into reusable component skills. Also interested in technological aids for education and healthcare in under-resourced environments such as South Africa.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="/images/people/riaan.jpg" alt="Riaan Stopforth" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Riaan Stopforth</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">Search &amp; Rescue · Prosthetics</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            Associate Professor at the University of KwaZulu-Natal heading the Stopforth Mechatronics, Robotics and Research Lab. Known for bridging advanced robotics with practical implementation through the Touch Hand project. Chair of the IEEE South Africa Joint RA/CS Chapter.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="https://www.raillab.org/author/steven-james/avatar_hud4d5d3cadb472fb09d290f604ae02aa9_27870_270x270_fill_lanczos_center_3.png" alt="Steven James" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Steven James</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">RL · Representation Learning</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            Senior Lecturer and Deputy Director of the RAIL Lab at the University of the Witwatersrand. Interested in developing generally intelligent agents capable of learning their own representations of tasks for planning.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="https://benedictquartey.github.io/assets/images/profile.jpg" alt="Benedict Quartey" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Benedict Quartey</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">LLMs · Robot Instruction</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            PhD from Brown University working on robotics and machine learning, including the use of LLMs for robot instruction. Interned at the Boston Dynamics AI Institute and served as Faculty Engagement Chair for the Deep Learning Indaba. Co-founder of Papermap AI.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
        <img src="https://www.raillab.org/author/branden-ingram/avatar_hu9cdac0a1ebb0ff79c33cf7ccee12cb20_52277_270x270_fill_q75_lanczos_center.jpg" alt="Branden Ingram" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Branden Ingram</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300/70 uppercase tracking-wide">ML · Games · Robotics</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
            Lecturer in Computer Science at the University of the Witwatersrand. His research sits at the intersection of machine learning, video games, and robotics. Contributes to the RAIL Lab and MIND Institute, and co-leads the Wits RoboCup team.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="reveal panel rounded-3xl p-8 mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-slate-400">
        Additional keynote speakers and tutorial leads will be announced as the programme is finalised.
        If you are interested in speaking or leading a session, please reach out via our Discord or email.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Organising Committee -->
    <div class="reveal mb-4">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-orange-300/90">Organising Committee</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">The team making it happen</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-400">
        The summer school is being organized by dedicated researchers and community builders committed to advancing robotics education and research across Africa.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal relative mt-12">
      <button
        id="organizers-prev"
        aria-label="Previous"
        class="absolute -left-4 top-1/2 z-10 hidden -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-2 text-white backdrop-blur hover:bg-white/10 lg:flex"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
      </button>
      <button
        id="organizers-next"
        aria-label="Next"
        class="absolute -right-4 top-1/2 z-10 hidden -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-2 text-white backdrop-blur hover:bg-white/10 lg:flex"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </button>

      <div
        id="organizers-track"
        class="flex gap-5 overflow-x-auto pb-4 [scroll-snap-type:x_mandatory] [scrollbar-width:none] [-ms-overflow-style:none] [&::-webkit-scrollbar]:hidden"
      >
        

        <div class="reveal w-[60vw] shrink-0 sm:w-[40vw] lg:w-[calc(20%-1rem)] [scroll-snap-align:start]">
          <div class="panel flex h-full flex-col items-center rounded-2xl p-5 text-center">
            <img src="/images/people/tamlin.jpg" alt="Tamlin Love" class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover" />
